snippet.title: CODE VEIN - Butterfly of Delirium Boss Trailer | X1, PS4, PC
snippet.description:
A poisonous pollinator, the Butterfly of Delirium is a vicious enemy with range and flight. 

Test your combinations of Gifts and Blood Codes in battle when #CODEVEIN releases on September 27th. Pre-Order today: https://bandainam.co/codevein
